@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_remfio(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (tmp + wp.exp((v1 + 0.19 + tmp + 0.33)))
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.45 / v0 + 0.46) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.69)) * 0.47)
    data[tid] = v0
